item.description:
We implement Change Impact Analysis on the library upgrade scenario, where we try to find out the client classes affected by a library upgrade.
This experiment is done to implement a light-weight solution for the upgrade compatibility checking problem:
Using facts and query scripts to find out the client classes affected by the library upgrade;
Running facts-guided test generation, i.e., guide test generator (EvoSuite was used) to only use these affected test classes as the test targets;
